            <ab>(Section 1): "To the account of the gold assessment  for the use of mules in transport: 1/3 1/12 gram . . .";(Section 2): "And to the account of the tax for vestis militaris on 19 1/6 arouras in all: 1/12 chlamys, 1/8 tunic, 1/90 pallium."</ab>
